OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome bright, sunny spells first
OL,6,Fthing. Then cloudier for a time with
OL,7,Fsome showers, wintry on high ground.
OL,8,FBright spells and showers in the
OL,9,Fafternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA few showers this evening,
OL,12,Fstill wintry on high ground, then
OL,13,Fbecoming dry overnight with clear
OL,14,Fspells. Winds easing and allowing a
OL,15,Ftouch of frost.
OL,16,
OL,17,CMonday:FA dry and bright day with
OL,18,Fplenty of sunshine, the best in the
OL,19,Fmorning with some high cloud arriving
OL,20,Fin the afternoon. Lighter winds, a
OL,21,Fgentle southerly later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
